{"tid":701142,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"重溫雷神2010年世界盃神蹟","createTime":"2018-06-14T01:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T04:14:57.000Z","uid":3373,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b6281a981d0ca40b877bf5350c4f89f33dec7687","tid":701142,"uid":3373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"2010果時既雷神唔係揸槌果個，係雷達<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雷達（高登會員編號：247518），高登會員之一，好賭成性，2010年南非世界盃分組賽期間預測賽果，卻十賭九輸，令他極速上位。<br />\n<br />\n2010年世界盃期間，雷達曾數次下注(每次俱聲稱以三位/四位數字下注)，甫開始便以賭7次輸足7次轟動高登[4]。其後更變成只要提及該隊，不論有否下注，該隊都會有相反的結果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E9%9B%B7%E9%81%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%259B%25B7%25E9%2581%2594&d=jSaVrvWmoXwvmhgKSppV049%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=cbff92b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E9%9B%B7%E9%81%94</a>"},{"pid":"7562e6420268762ee05e5d8f4e773f404cf643f0","tid":701142,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T01:47:29.000Z","msg":"雷神 vs 桂神"},{"pid":"04532dc5e78c82a4dc09e97e3a3961e575a9b7d7","tid":701142,"uid":41524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T01:48:33.000Z","msg":"經典!"},{"pid":"54619859eaba1b346bcbb30e41e9a2832ef69f1c","tid":701142,"uid":3373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T01:52:22.000Z","msg":"期待今年有神打救世人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3177f47cb5a3f585e7163daaa126f3b4e5c7c683","tid":701142,"uid":119729,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T02:25:07.000Z","msg":"記得有場話天氣好好,<br />\n之後下半場即刻落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1dc24038e738fc35842d538392fed6b6b5a0c2a","tid":701142,